groups.title: SIGABA A: INDZABA
groups.instructions: Bhala indzaba NGASINYE saletihloko letilandzelako ibe ngemagama la-340 kuya kula-390.

questions.text: Bafundzi abakhokhele tindleko tesikolo. Vumela nobe uphikise lesitatimende.

Khetsa SINYE saletitfombe letilandzelako bese ubhala indzaba ngesihloko loticabangele sona. Bhala inombolo yembuto (1.6, 1.7 NOBE 1.8). Nika indzaba yakho sihloko lesifanele. CAPHELA: Akube nekubumbana emkhatsini wendzaba nesitfombe losikhetsile.
questions.context: Isitfombe lesikhombisa imicibisholo neminde/itrophy letinhlobonhlobo (inkhanyezi, indebe, umhlaba) letibekwe etikweto.

groups.title: SIGABA B: EMATHEKSTHI EMIBHALOMBIKO
groups.instructions: Khetsa KUBILI kulokulandzelako ubhale ngako ngemagama la-100 kuya kula-120 itheksthi ngayinye.

questions.text:
INKHULUMOMPHENDVULWANO

Gogo wakho uyacala kutfola imali yempesheni. Ukucela kutsi ujabule naye. Bhala inkhulumomphendvulwano lesemkhatsini wakho naye.

UMLANDVOMUFI

Kushone umsakati lobekavakashela kakhulu ummango wangakini. Bhala umlandvomufi lotawufundvwa ngelilanga lekumfihla.

INCWADZI YEBUHLOBO

Umnakenu sewugule kakhulu wate wayekela kunatsa emaphilisi ngoba abona shangatsi akamsiti. Bhala incwadzi umkhutsate.

SIHLATIYWA

Bewulalele umdlalo wemoya lodlala onkhe emalanga emsakatweni. Bhala sihlatiywa salenkhundla loyilalele.

INCWADZI YEMTSETFO

Likamelo locashe kulo lelisedvute nesikolo lofundza kuso, ulitfole ligcwele emanti ngenca yemvula lebekhona, wonakalelwe timphahla. Bhalela umninindzawo incwadzi umatise ngalesehlakalo.

UMBIKO

Benimeme baculi emmangweni wangakini nitewutfutfukisa sikhwama senhlangano yelusha, wena njengemhlelembisi walomcimbi bhalela sihlalo umbiko umatise kutsi kuhambe njani.
